column2: SELECT   sg.ID, sg.ra as ra_i, s.ra, sg.dec as dec_i, s.dec, sg.logMstarPhot,      n.objid, n.distance * #. as distance, log1#(n.distance * #.) as log_distance,        s.z, s.zErr,   s.velDisp, s.velDispErr,   s.snMedian,      l.sigmaStars, l.sigmaStarsErr, l.chisq, l.bpt,   l.EW_Hb_#, l.EW_Hb_#_Err, l.Flux_Hb_#, l.Flux_Hb_#_Err, l.Flux_Cont_Hb_#, l.Flux_Cont_Hb_#_Err,   l.EW_Ha_#, l.EW_Ha_#_Err, l.Flux_Ha_#, l.Flux_Ha_#_Err, l.Flux_Cont_Ha_#, l.Flux_Cont_Ha_#_Err,   l.V_Ha_#, l.V_Ha_#_Err, l.Sigma_Ha_#, l.Sigma_Ha_#_Err,      mpa.lgm_tot_p5# as lgm, (mpa.lgm_tot_p8#-mpa.lgm_tot_p1#)/#. as lgm_Err,   mpa.sfr_tot_p5# as lsfr, (mpa.sfr_tot_p8#-mpa.sfr_tot_p1#)/#. as lsfr_Err,   mpa.bptclass as mpa_bpt    INTO mydb.SHADE_kinematics FROM MyDB.SHADE_radec AS sg CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(sg.ra, sg.dec, #) AS n JOIN SpecObj AS s ON n.objid=s.bestobjid   JOIN emissionLinesPort as l ON s.specobjid=l.specobjid JOIN galSpecExtra as mpa on s.specobjid=mpa.specobjid
